[[File:Bahrain International Air Show 2012 Day 2.jpg|thumb|Photograph from the 2012 edition of the airshow.]] The '''Bahrain International Airshow''' is a biennial [[airshow]] hosted at the [[Sakhir Air Base]] in the [[Kingdom of Bahrain]]. The event is organised by the [[Civil Aviation Affairs|Civil Aviation Affairs of Bahrain]] in association with [[Farnborough Airshow|Farnborough International]], and is sponsored by [[Gulf Air]] and [[Batelco]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Bahrain International Airshow takes off today|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/bahrain-international-airshow-takes-off-today/1218663|publisher=The Financial Express|accessdate=16 January 2014}}</ref>
Since its inception in 2010, the airshow has drawn hundreds of companies and tens of thousands of visitors.<ref name=GDN>{{cite news|title=Bahrain air show set to take off...|url=http://www.gulf-daily-news.com/NewsDetails.aspx?storyid=367093|accessdate=16 January 2014|newspaper=Gulf Daily News|date=19 December 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=HRH Crown Prince opens Bahrain International Airshow 2014|url=http://www.bna.bh/portal/en/news/598029|publisher=Bahrain News Agency|accessdate=16 January 2014}}</ref>
